node.text: 3 years is a crazy concept… not a day goes by where i don’t think about how life would be if u didn’t go. i swear ur presence is eternal, so impactful that we all can still feel you here from time to time. the whole world is a little less sunny without you in it.. but that comes with endless gratitude for the things u taught us by simply existing. always and forever THE goat. stream Mac Miller a little extra this week- rest in paradise, Malcolm
